Flash Briefing Skill

des: Listen to daily updates from the Arundel News Network, exclusively from the ANN studios in Anne arundel County, Maryland. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
